docs/spike-notes.md

# Local runtime / backup artifacts
.omc/sessions/
config/*.bak
config/*.bak*
config/*backup

# Operational agent state (transient; never committed)
.agents/
.oma/
.omc/
.omx/
.graphwiki/
graphwiki-out/
